{"tid":941111,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"最後都係分開","createTime":"2018-12-14T13:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T17:08:45.000Z","uid":132434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e253cfdd1de1167d09be9db17f00998db45d4dc2","tid":941111,"uid":132434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:26:05.000Z","msg":"退後一步更發現 原來一直不被珍惜<br />\n無論係我既付出 定係我 喺對方眼中都係一文不值<br />\n小小要求 都係奢求<br />\n我只想要安全感 顧我感受 珍惜我<br />\n原來 生日要件蛋糕係過分<br />\n要佢同女仔保持距離係過分<br />\n已經三翻四次俾機會<br />\n唔係我唔願讓步 <br />\n我承認 每人都有雙重標準既地方<br />\n佢講既 我可以盡力做<br />\n但<br />\n我講既 佢可以用所有藉口推卸<br />\n每人都有自己重視既點 呢點可以理解<br />\n但佢總覺得我唔知足<br />\n懶係人都有 但係咪錫自己<br />\n真係感受到<br />\n我唔係要錢 要物質<br />\n要關心 同上心就夠<br />\n喊 俾人反問有咩好喊<br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649711de6913727107d5f15cd90e631e2dccd58d","tid":941111,"uid":66436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:26:29.000Z","msg":"系..."},{"pid":"a073043ef7c9d832a64cab9aa33bd2cc078f6b56","tid":941111,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"649711de6913727107d5f15cd90e631e2dccd58d","tid":941111,"uid":66436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:26:29.000Z","msg":"系..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T17:08:45.000Z","msg":".......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}